OL,6,FPublisher Puffin said it was taking
OL,7,Fthe matter extremely seriously and was
OL,8,Fworking to get the website removed.
OL,10,FThe explicit content prompted a number
OL,11,Fof schools to contact parents making
OL,12,Fthem aware of the issue, as well as
OL,13,Fremoving books from library shelves.
OL,15,FOne email seen by ITV News included a
OL,16,Fgraphic showing which books were
OL,17,Faffected and advised parents to
OL,18,F"remove them immediately".
