OL,6,FIt said the link shows "inappropriate
OL,7,Fand unsafe material, which contains
OL,8,Fhighly pornographic content with no
OL,9,Fage restriction".
OL,11,FThe email added that any books owned
OL,12,Fby the school should be returned so
OL,13,Fstaff can dispose of them.
OL,15,FIn a joint statement, Andrew Cope and
OL,16,FPuffin Books, said: "In some editions
OL,17,Fof the Spy Dog, Spy Cat and Spy Pups
OL,18,Fseries there is a reference to the
OL,19,Fauthor, Andrew Cope's, former website
OL,20,Ffor the series which was owned and
OL,21,Fmanaged by him.
