OL,6,F"We understand an unconnected third
OL,7,Fparty has very recently taken control
OL,8,Fof the domain name and is using it to
OL,9,Fdisplay a different website with
OL,10,Finappropriate adult content.
OL,12,F"This website is not associated with
OL,13,FPuffin or Andrew Cope. We are asking
OL,14,Fpeople not to visit the website and
OL,15,Fensure that children do not visit it
OL,16,Feither.
