OL,6,FWe are taking this extremely seriously
OL,7,Fand are acting on this issue as a
OL,8,Fmatter of urgency through the
OL,9,Fappropriate channels to get this
OL,10,Fwebsite removed.
OL,12,F"This is an in-depth and complex legal
OL,13,Fprocess and will take time. In
OL,14,Faddition we have immediately paused on
OL,15,Fthe sale and distribution of the books
OL,16,Fwhilst we deal with this matter.
OL,18,F"We are currently working with retail
OL,19,Fand education and library partners to
OL,20,Fremove the books from shelves for the
OL,21,Ftime being.
