OL,6,F"We are asking anyone who has copies
OL,7,Fof these titles to remove these books
OL,8,Ffrom their shelves."
OL,10,FA spokesperson for Nominet, which runs
OL,11,Fthe .UK registry, said: "We have
OL,12,Fsuspended this website for breaching
OL,13,Four terms and conditions. The website
OL,14,Fdid not conduct suitable age
OL,15,Fverification as required under the
OL,16,FOnline Safety Act - and we have
OL,17,Fadvised the domain owner and its
OL,18,Fregistrar.
